; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">38. </span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">传热系数<span lang=\"EN-US\">K W/( m2.K)overall heat transfer coefficient</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">稳态条件下，围护结构两侧空气温差为<span lang=\"EN-US\">1K</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">1h</span>内通过<span lang=\"EN-US\">1m2</span>面积传递的热量</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">39. </span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">传热阻<span lang=\"EN-US\">R0 m2.K /W</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">传热系数的倒数</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">40. </span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">围护结构<span lang=\"EN-US\"> building envelope</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">建筑物及房间各面的围挡物，如墙体、屋顶、地板、地面和门窗等。分内、外围护结构两类。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>','','','','','','',2,NULL,1,'1',0,0,'2012-05-14 15:30:16','2012-05-14 15:30:16','f372ad8e60a732ad22bc837ba962a5de'),(23,4,26,'聚氨酯，喷涂，保温隔热，保护层','','聚氨酯喷涂及保护层','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">保温隔热材料采用聚氨酯喷涂的越来越多，这种保温材料并不具备抗裂能力，如基层或其表面的保护层产生裂缝，都会波及到聚氨酯保温材料的正常使用，加速它的老化，影响它的保温性能及耐久性。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\">聚氨酯表面保护层的材料，以往通常在其底部砌<span lang=\"EN-US\">120mm</span>厚砖墙，或用薄壁混凝土或做钢丝网抹灰，即解决了底部防撞又起到保护层的作用。上部保护层的材料一般喷涂聚氨酯漆。如果按墙体底部保护层的做法，存在施工周期长，工程量大，使用寿命短的问题。在喷涂聚氨酯保温材料表面，使用高分子材料类弹性涂料进行保护，是一种十分经济有效的手段。（墙体防撞保护可做防撞栏杆）。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 27pt; tab-stops: list 27.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">⑴</span><span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\">弹性保护涂层的选择依据</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\">弹性涂料是指伸长率在<span lang=\"EN-US\">100%</span>以上且能恢复原状的涂料。除此而外，弹性保护层还有以下用途：<span lang=\"EN-US\">a.</span>阻碍湿气透过；<span lang=\"EN-US\">b.</span>提高整体的抗冲击性和耐磨性；<span lang=\"EN-US\">c.</span>提高美观效果；<span lang=\"EN-US\"> d. </span>达到阻燃和相关环保法的要求。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 31.5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">由于弹性涂料必须完全粘接在聚氨酯表面并且成为绝热系统的必备部分，在选择弹性涂料时，应考虑以下几个方面：<span lang=\"EN-US\">a.</span>涂料的物理特性，包括耐化学性、水蒸汽透过性、撕裂强度和伸长率、耐老化性能；<span lang=\"EN-US\">b.</span>涂料的使用性能，包括使用环境，使用期，与聚氨酯的附着力，燃烧性能（包括自身的燃烧性能及同聚氨酯泡沫复合后的燃烧性能），美观效果和隔汽层的选择等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 27pt; tab-stops: list 9.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">⑵</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\">弹性保护涂料的种类和性能</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 27pt; tab-stops: list 9.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">⑶</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">丁基橡胶是一种弹性体，同其它弹性体相比，具有非常低的水蒸汽透过率，所以适用于蒸汽压差特别大的区域，适合于做冷库的隔汽层及聚氨酯的保护层，施工厚度不<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span>小于<span lang=\"EN-US\">1mm</span>。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 23.65pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">氯丁橡胶涂料可以作为冷库隔汽层及聚氨酯保护层，但温度不能低于<span lang=\"EN-US\">-18</span>℃，否则它的弹性会降低。施工要求材料厚度不小于<span lang=\"EN-US\">1mm</span>。</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">聚氨酯弹性涂料，分芳香族和脂肪族两大类，芳香族长期暴露易变黄和粉化，通常作为脂肪族聚氨酯的底层，脂肪族聚氨酯没有变色现象，通常作面漆使用。施工要求材料厚度不小于<span lang=\"EN-US\">1mm</span>。该涂料的缺点是普通聚氨酯对底材表面潮气和水敏感。</span></p>','','','','','','',2,NULL,0,'1',0,0,'2012-05-14 15:43:32',