 15:59:45','be6c7c5b0de526d3bf75ef6543cdc77c'),(25,4,26,'EPS（聚苯）夹芯板，XPS挤塑聚苯乙烯夹芯板，PU夹芯板，硬质聚氨酯夹芯板，RW夹芯板，岩棉夹芯板','','保温夹芯板的适用温度范围','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: -8.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 26.9pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: -.85; mso-para-margin-left: 1.71gd;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1.EPS</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">（聚苯）夹芯板</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"> <br /><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">从理论上讲<span lang=\"EN-US\">EPS</span>板可以在<span lang=\"EN-US\">-80</span>℃～<span lang=\"EN-US\">+70<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">℃</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">的范围内使用，但就EPS</span></span>夹芯板的构造而言，它不适于在温度过低的冷库中使用。在做低温冷库尤其是大型冷库时，板缝中间易有凝露现象产生，如果用于低温冷库，要注意解决板缝连接的问题。建议用于常温及高温库。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: -8.9pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 26.85pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: -.85; mso-para-margin-left: 1.71gd;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: -8.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 26.9pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: -.85; mso-para-margin-left: 1.71gd;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2.</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">挤塑聚苯乙烯夹芯板，即<span lang=\"EN-US\">XPS</span>夹芯板</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>XPS</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">与<span lang=\"EN-US\">EPS</span>都为聚苯乙烯，但生产工艺不一样，<span lang=\"EN-US\">XPS</span>为挤压式而<span lang=\"EN-US\">EPS</span>为发泡式，所以其适用温度范围、制成夹芯板的工艺、需要注意的问题是一样的。但<span lang=\"EN-US\">XPS</span>的抗压性、憎水性都优于<span lang=\"EN-US\">EPS</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">XPS</span>的块材更适于低温库的地面、墙面、屋面保温。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /><br /><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3.PU</span></strong></span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">夹芯板</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">硬质聚氨酯夹芯板，理论上讲可以在<span lang=\"EN-US\">-110</span>℃～<span lang=\"EN-US\">+120<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">℃</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">范围内使用，但低于-60<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">℃</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">时建议金属面板要为不锈钢板为好；在高于+95<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">℃</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">时要改用高温型聚氨酯发泡料，不然高温情况下夹芯板会胀裂，槽口接缝处会变形严重。做超低温库要特别注意。</span></span></span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: -8.9pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 26.85pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: -.85; mso-para-margin-left: 1.71gd;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: -8.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 26.9pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: -.85; mso-para-margin-left: 1.71gd;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">4.RW</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">夹芯板</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">岩棉夹芯板，简称<span lang=\"EN-US\">RW</span>夹芯板。岩棉为不燃性材料<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>其导热系数为<span lang=\"EN-US\">0.034</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">0.045,</span>其使用温度范围为<span lang=\"EN-US\">-60</span>℃～<span lang=\"EN-US\">+500<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">℃</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">。国内生产的岩棉夹芯板,</span></span>其板内普遍使用金属支撑架，做低温库有问题。但国外生产的岩棉夹芯板及国内合资不用金属做支撑的岩棉夹心板，做低温冷库是没问题的。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: -8.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 26.9pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: -.85; mso-para-margin-left: 1.71gd;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: -8.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 26.9pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: -.85; mso-para-margin-left: 1.71gd;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: -8.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 26.9pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: -.85; mso-para-margin-left: 1.71gd;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: -8.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 26.9pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: -.85; mso-para-margin-left: 1.71gd;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>','','','','','','',2,NULL,1,'1',0,0,'2012-05-14 16:06:24','2012-05-14 16:06:24','51867c8e1f25dc8ceb013aa6fb199596'),(26,3,21,'工程造价，直接费，间接费，直接工程费，措施费，规费，企业管理费','','建筑安装工程费用组成表','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;\">中国现行<a name=\"OLE_LINK1\"></a>建筑安装工程费用组成表</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 9pt;\">（从<span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>日起）</span></p>\r\n<div align=\"center\">\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"margin: auto auto auto 4